data.description: Looking for a Large Lot? Need an income property near UC Merced? You've found it! Located in the sought-after Via Moraga neighborhood near UC Merced, shopping, and Lake Yosemite, this modern 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home stands out with its features and prime location. Built in 2021, it's set on a generous 8,100 sq ft lot, offering space and comfort. The interior boasts an open-concept kitchen with a spacious island and ample storage, ideal for culinary adventures. The main living area, with large windows overlooking the backyard, provides a perfect blend of relaxation and entertainment. Offering three bedrooms upstairs and one downstairs, the house supports various living arrangements, accommodating a growing family or a roommate setup. Notably, the house is a short walk from two local parks, enhancing its appeal. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity - book your tour today!
